- Install LibreElec img to SD via DD
- Put update package(http://forum.kodi.tv/showthread.php?tid=269814) into .update folder, and reboot pi
- Move to /tmp, run getwidevine.sh
- Copy amazon repo .zip to raspi
- Install repo from zip
- Install Amazon VOD plugin from repo
- Settings:
	- English
	- Use InputStream to play video, not browsers
	- Add credentials
